@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "_StorefrontLayout";
}

<div class="sf-page">
    <div class="sf-prose">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="sf-prose-sub">Last updated: November 2026</p>

        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
            WebshopShop is a school project built as part of an apprenticeship final exam (LAP).
            It is not a live commercial service. This page describes how data would be handled
            in a real deployment of the application.
        </p>

        <h2>What we collect</h2>
        <p>
            When you register an account, we store your email address and an encrypted password hash.
            When you place an order, we store the items purchased, the total amount, and the shipping
            and billing address you provide at checkout.
        </p>

        <h2>How we use it</h2>
        <p>
            Account data is used to authenticate you and to display your order history. Order data
            is used to fulfill purchases and to generate invoice PDFs. We do not share data with
            third parties.
        </p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>
            Under the GDPR, you have the right to access, correct, and delete your personal data.
            Account deletion can be requested through your account settings.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
            This is a school project. For real applications operated commercially, a real contact
            address and Datenschutzbeauftragter would be listed here.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>